snippet.title: Shaq Fu: A Legend Reborn - Mobile Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Shaq Fu: A Legend Reborn NOW on iOS and Android smartphones and tablets!  Fight your way through the streets as none other than Shaq Fu himself, voiced by the real deal, Shaquille O’Neal!

iOS:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/shaq-fu-a-legend-reborn/id1255910488?mt=8&ign-mpt=uo%3D4

Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.maddog.shaqfu
